Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.15,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs30\shad0\bord0\an3\c&HADAB92&\b1\pos(350.802,638.799)}Kawasaki   Yokohama       Kannai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.85,Subtitles,Kathrina subs,0,0,0,,It's basically a maze...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.31,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Konnichiwa! Um, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.44,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Guten Tag? {\fnArial}Добрый день{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.44,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Bonjour?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.14,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Merci!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.20,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That means "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:37.29,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Guten Tag. I'm German, but you \Ncan speak to me in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:43.67,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,So... where are you headed? \NI'll be happy to show you the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.72,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.84,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Asakusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.31,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Asakusa?! We're headed there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:51.87,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Come on! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.71,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.44,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(753.6,573.198)\org(753,573)\fscx97.364\fscy100\frz0\fry-4.751\fax0\fnArial\fs36\b1\xbord3.8\ybord3.9\3c&H7F52A9&}Won't You Be a {\c&H4B35BE&\3c&HE1E4FC&}Dai Star, {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7F52A9&}too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, what did you come to see today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:03.69,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.60,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're going to Asakusa, \Nso I figure you're seeing a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.89,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It has over a hundred theaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.16,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Is anything super popular right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:15.16,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(301.2,379.8)\fnLato\b1\c&H2D2546&\3a&HFF&\blur0.5}Did you make it to Japan safely?\NTell me if you pass or fail your audition immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:15.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Maybe... {\i1}Mecha Macbeth Versus Space Hamlet{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.38,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, what is it, Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.79,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.12,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.22,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,When's the train coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.42,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,It'll be here soon. Just keep \Nreading your picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(995.199,229.2)\fnImpact\fscx200\c&H231AD7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3}Little Red Riding Hood
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.18,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Do you like "Little Red Riding Hood"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.59,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.24,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Then I'll perform it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.74,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you an actress, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:50.98,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh... Not yet, but I hope to be someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.01,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes.
