Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.13,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Welcome to Asakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.63,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh... It's much noisier \Nthan where I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.64,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Where you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.65,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Thanks for leading me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.09,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What? I can take you to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.98,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll use my navigation app from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.77,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see...
